@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - Alternative Three

autonumber

actor "Human Resources\nManager" as GRH
participant ":System" as System

activate GRH

    GRH -> System : asks to create a new profession
        activate System

            System --> GRH : requests data (i.e. designation, descriptions,\nmedium salary)
        deactivate System

        GRH -> System : types requested data
        activate System

            System --> GRH : shows a list of required education levels and\nasks to select one
        deactivate System

        GRH -> System : selects a required level of education
        activate System

                System --> GRH : shows a list of competences and asks you\nto select all the ones you need
        deactivate System

        GRH -> System : selects all the necessary competences
        activate System

                System --> GRH : presents a list of sectors of activity\nand asks you to select one
        deactivate System

        GRH -> System : selects a sector of activity
        activate System

            System --> GRH : shows all data and requests confirmation
        deactivate System

        GRH -> System : not confirm data
        activate System

            System --> GRH : returns the data and asks for revision
        deactivate System

        GRH -> System : review and change the desired data
        activate System

            System --> GRH : shows all data and requests confirmation
        deactivate System

        GRH -> System : confirms data
        activate System

            System --> GRH : displays operation success
        deactivate System

@enduml